<a href="/contact"><button type="button" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap font-medium focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 transition-colors h-8 px-3 text-xs rounded-md bg-primary text-primary-foreground border border-primary-border hover:bg-primary/90 shadow-lg shadow-primary/20 hover:shadow-xl" aria-label="Get a Quote"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-phone w-4 h-4"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"></path></svg>Get a Quote</button></a></div><button id="mobile-menu-toggle" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="mobile-menu" class="md:hidden p-2 text-slate-600" aria-label="Toggle menu"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-menu w-6 h-6"><line x1="4" x2="20" y1="12" y2="12"></line><line x1="4" x2="20" y1="6" y2="6"></line><line x1="4" x2="20" y1="18" y2="18"></line></svg></button></div><div id="mobile-menu" class="md:hidden hidden border-t border-slate-200 bg-white" aria-hidden="true"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-4 flex flex-col gap-3"><a href="/" class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 hover:text-primary py-2">Home</a><a href="/services" class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 hover:text-primary py-2">Services</a><a href="/about" class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 hover:text-primary py-2">About</a><a href="/blog" class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 hover:text-primary py-2">Field Notes</a><a href="/contact" class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 hover:text-primary py-2">Contact</a><a href="/contact" class="mt-2 inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap font-medium rounded-md border border-emerald-500/50 text-emerald-700 hover:bg-emerald-50 min-h-8 px-3 text-xs py-2">Encrypted Inquiry</a><a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap font-medium rounded-md bg-primary text-primary-foreground min-h-8 px-3 text-xs py-2">Get a Quote</a></div></div></nav><main class="flex-grow"><div class="pt-20"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 py-16 md:py-24"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center mb-24"><div><span class="text-primary font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase text-sm">About Us</span><h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-2 mb-6 leading-tight">We Are PlausiDen LLC</h1><p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">Founded on the principle that technology should be an enabler, not a barrier, PlausiDen provides IT solutions that are both broad in scope and precise in execution.</p><p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">Our name represents our commitment to plausible, practical, and potent solutions. We don't just fix computers; we engineer the digital foundations upon which modern enterprises are built.</p><div class="flex gap-4"><a href="/contact"><button class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap text-sm font-medium focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-ring disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:size-4 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 hover-elevate active-elevate-2 bg-primary text-primary-foreground border border-primary-border min-h-10 rounded-xl px-8">Contact Us</button></a><a href="/services"><button class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap text-sm font-medium focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-ring disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:size-4 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 hover-elevate active-elevate-2 border [border-color:var(--button-outline)] shadow-xs active:shadow-none min-h-10 rounded-xl px-8">View Services</button></a></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary/10 rounded-3xl transform rotate-3"></div><img src="/static/images/hero-architecture.jpg" alt="Modern corporate architecture" class="relative rounded-3xl shadow-2xl w-full h-auto object-cover border border-slate-100"></div></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-24"><div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100"><h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Our Mission</h3><p class="text-slate-600">To deliver high-quality, reliable, and innovative IT solutions that empower businesses to operate securely and efficiently in a digital-first world.</p></div><div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100"><h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Our Vision</h3><p class="text-slate-600">To be the trusted technology partner for enterprises seeking to navigate the complexities of IT operations, security, and automation.</p></div><div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100"><h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Our Approach</h3><p class="text-slate-600">General yet specific. We offer a holistic view of your IT ecosystem while applying specialized expertise to every component.</p></div></div><div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto"><h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8">Core Values</h2><div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 text-left"><div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-white p-4 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100"><div class="bg-primary/10 p-1 rounded-full"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check w-4 h-4 text-primary"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg></div><span class="font-medium text-slate-800">Integrity in every interaction</span></div><div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-white p-4 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100"><div class="bg-primary/10 p-1 rounded-full"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check w-4 h-4 text-primary"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg></div><span class="font-medium text-slate-800">Excellence in technical execution</span></div><div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-white p-4 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100"><div class="bg-primary/10 p-1 rounded-full"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check w-4 h-4 text-primary"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg></div><span class="font-medium text-slate-800">Innovation that drives value</span></div><div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-white p-4 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100"><div class="bg-primary/10 p-1 rounded-full"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check w-4 h-4 text-primary"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg></div><span class="font-medium text-slate-800">Security as a foundational element</span></div></div></div></div></div></main><footer class="bg-slate-900 text-slate-300 py-16"><div class